comments: Professor Gladish is the best professor I have had this semester. She is very clear, helpful and is very inspiring to make you want to succeed in this course. I learned so much about music and even learned how to create my own music score. I definitely recommend her.

SHE IS A FANTASTIC TEACHER! She\'s funny, understanding, and really has a passion for music as well as the students\' comprehension. I wish she would teach the upper level music theories. She puts everything on Blackboard so unless you\'re a slacker, this class is super easy AND understanding. I highly recommend her!
She Is Super Nice And Is Always Willing To Help When Needed! Take Her!

I took her for Music Fundamentals. I am currently in her class and my grade is seriously a 101.7. She gives tons of extra credit and is super helpful. I would definetly recommend taking her class for your fine arts credit.
